    "media:imagetext": "Complete set of menus\nsuitable for framing may be\nobtained upon request\nmenu\nCover Design\nby Lillian Sader.\nCover Design\nby Lillian Sader.\nOne of America's leading\nyoung artists, Miss Sader\ncombines a deft color touch\nwith a sensilive flair\nfor intricate design.\nFor the South Pacific\nshe has created\na unique tableau of\nthese famous attractions-\nTypical Fijian Village\nFijian Fisherman\nKoala Bear\nAboriginal Bark Drawings\nKangaroo, Boomerang\nHand-carved Gateway of Maori Pa\nMaori Wood Carver\nKiwi Bird\nChilled Orange Juice\nCheese Omelet, American\nGrilled Lean Bacon Strips\nPetite Danish\nButter\nMuffins\nJelly\nCoffee\nTea\nMilk\nPAN AMERICAN WORLD AIRWAYSE\nPRINTED IN U.S. A.",
